These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, snowmobile, van, taxi
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, sunflower, balloon-flower, aconite, iris
1. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsaconite is in the middle##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the tram is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
6. the person driving the taxi is in the middle##1
7. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
8. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Transport          | motorbike | tram | taxi | van | snowmobile |
| Flower   | balloon-flower  | iris      | aconite   | lily     | sunflower    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, apricot, green, coral, chestnut
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, western, satire, epic, martial-arts
1. the person who likes black is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes black is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is in the middle##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
5. the person watching scientific movies is between the person who likes green and the person watching epic movies##2
6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who likes black##1
7. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Color   | green     | coral       | chestnut    | black | apricot   |
| Movie-Genre      | western | scientific | epic | martial-arts      | satire |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, animation, adventure, mystery, fantasy
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, havana, bluemaster, aristoff, bongani
1. the aristoff-smoker is the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
6. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
7. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific | adventure | animation | mystery    | fantasy |
| Cigar   | aristoff     | davidoff        | bluemaster      | havana | bongani      |

