.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, yellow, azure, red, lilac
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, bird, chinchilla, ferret, horse
1. the person who likes azure is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes lilac is the owner of the bird##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
6. the person who likes yellow is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who likes lilac##2
7. the owner of the horse is the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Color         | light-blue      | red | azure | yellow   | lilac  |
| Pet   | ferret | horse    | chinchilla        | goldfish | bird |

