.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie, disaster, action, mystery
5 different games are played: whist, billiard, mah-jongg, snooker, poker
1. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
5. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
7. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
8. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Movie-Genre      | mystery      | zombie | thriller   | action  | disaster  |
| Game   | mah-jongg | snooker | whist | billiard | poker |

