.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, lavender, chestnut, aquamarine, emerald
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, gospel, jazz, soul, pop
1. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
2. the fan of gospel is between the fan of pop and the person who likes chestnut##2
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
5. the fan of jazz is the person who likes chestnut##1
6. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
8. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Color   | lavender        | black                | aquamarine  | chestnut  | emerald            |
| Music-Genre        | house | pop | gospel | jazz | soul |

