.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, baccarat, fonseca, oliveros, aristoff
5 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, mouse, ferret, lizard
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
6. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
8. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
9. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Cigar   | aristoff       | fonseca   | baccarat    | oliveros    | ritmeester |
| Pet        | mouse | snake | rabbit | lizard | ferret     |

