.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: sailing, cricket, biathlon, skiing-polo, skiing
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, pakistani, german, french, malaysian
1. the german is the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the french##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing-polo is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the thai##1
5. the thai is between the french and the malaysian##2
6. the german is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the german is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Sport      | biathlon  | sailing       | cricket      | skiing-polo  | skiing   |
| Nationality   | malaysian | thai | french | pakistani | german |

