.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, social-worker, freelancer, musician, journalist
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, december, september, february, august
1. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
2. the musician is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the musician##1
4. the musician is on the far right##1
5. the social-worker is the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the freelancer is between the social-worker and the fisherman##2
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the freelancer##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Job   | journalist | social-worker | freelancer     | fisherman | musician |
| Birthday           | december | july     | september | august    | february      |

