2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is baking is the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
7. the person eating asparagus is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Food     | lime | tomato | asparagus | eggplant | pepper |
| Hobby   | video-games | collecting | gardening    | baking    | reading  |

