.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, pall-mall, siglo, chaman, bongani
5 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, fish, cat, snake
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the snake is the blend-smoker##1
3. the owner of the snake is in the middle##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
5. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the snake and the pall-mall-smoker##2
7. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
8. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
9. the owner of the snake is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar        | chaman | bongani | blend  | siglo | pall-mall     |
| Pet   | lizard  | fish     | snake | ferret      | cat |

