.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-13::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, september, february, march, august
City: nizza, berlin, rome, new-york, prague
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's birthday is in february##2
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
8. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Birthday      | august       | february | september | march   | may   |
| City   | new-york | berlin | prague  | nizza | rome |

