3. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
7. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who growsbellflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
