.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, trance, dubstep, d&b, rock
There 5 different types of food: apple, nectarine, watermelon, tomato, zucchini
1. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
2. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
3. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
5. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
6. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
7. the person eating watermelon is in an odd position##4
8. the person eating tomato is in the middle##1
9. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | dubstep    | d&b | salsa   | rock |
| Food   | zucchini | nectarine | tomato    | apple | watermelon |

