.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, tulip, bellflower, lily
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, fuchsia, turquise, light-blue, amber
1. the person who growsbellflower is the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growslily is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who likes red##2
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
7. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | bellflower | tulip     | lily     | daffodil |
| Color     | light-blue   | fuchsia   | red | turquise | amber  |

