.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
There are 5 different nationalities: egyptian, colombian, mexican, canadian, polish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, cycling, snowboarding, lacrosse, climbing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the polish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
5. the colombian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
8. the polish is on the left of the mexican##1
9. the mexican is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | colombian | polish     | mexican | canadian |
| Sport     | lacrosse       | cycling   | snowboarding | tennis   | climbing        |

