.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
5 different games are played: domino, monopoly, whist, poker, bridge
City: boston, rome, edinburgh, hamburg, miami
1. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
5. the person playing bridge is between the person playing domino and the person traveling to miami##2
6. the person traveling to rome is between the person playing poker and the person traveling to miami##2
7. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4
8. the person traveling to miami is the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Game         | poker | whist | monopoly | bridge | domino     |
| City   | hamburg    | rome   | miami       | edinburgh | boston |

