.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, fanta, coffee, sprite
City: san-francisco, boston, berlin, rome, nizza
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to rome##2
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | fanta      | coffee | sprite     | tea      |
| City     | nizza | boston | rome | san-francisco | berlin |

 